  <!-- Parenthesized noteheads (<notehead parentheses="yes">): a ghost/optional note. The
       notation part draws round brackets around the notehead; the tab part wraps the fret
       number in parentheses on the matching string. A plain note is interleaved so the
       parenthesized one reads against an un-bracketed neighbor.
